{"tid":1775054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請告訴我，遊行人數有咩意思？","createTime":"2019-12-08T15:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T04:04:11.000Z","uid":280746,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b596ebdb6a9e6dfc7f1d444b7c0ecfbb4d65ea1e","tid":1775054,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:10:26.000Z","msg":"遊行完咗再問大家<br />\n等大家可以係冷靜情況之後諗下<br />\n咁執着遊行人數，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人多就贏？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日我覺得最有意義嘅係火燒法院<br />\n參與人數唔多<br />\n效果勁，令到政府即刻譴責<br />\n而家冇人得閒理你的人數<br />\n搞咗半年都係戇鳩鳩咁<br />\n唔知自己衰咩嘅咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88edf13ba5b28b9a0de3bef2b566e0544b36896e","tid":1775054,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"搵一大堆藉口<br />\n話唔抗爭<br />\n等自己好落台<br />\n又有光環<br />\n<br />\n示威者冇組織係業餘<br />\n但旁觀者對示威者有好高要求<br />\n唔好阻塞交通，阻人返工<br />\n唔好整到女性，老人<br />\n<br />\n邊個仲會出嚟抗爭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f75dfc43d146a05ee8447bb0850b7ae850f17e","tid":1775054,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2de47b4ff9ad0dae4ec3ec69a9d5e4f39680b7","tid":1775054,"uid":280746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:39:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3916ee9672f8b42043144332f0d1597f4aab659a","tid":1775054,"uid":186010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5bdb5dc940cb47d5b8a2d464d5e1b45d7eaa6e",